# 🔐 boAt Login Page

This is the **Login UI** for the boAt Lifestyle project. It's a clean, responsive, and demo-ready login screen made using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**.

## 📸 Preview

> Elegant 2-column design with background image, password toggle, and smooth transitions.

## ✨ Features

- #ResponsiveLoginPage
- #EmailAndPasswordValidation
- #PasswordToggle (Show/Hide)
- #ClientSideValidation
- #ErrorHandling
- #LoadingSpinner
- #SuccessMessage
- #DemoLoginSupport
- #HTMLCSSJavaScript

## 👨‍💻 Demo Users

