❗ Only front-end validation and simulation is enabled (no backend auth connected)

📂 File Info
login.html – Main login page UI

Inline JavaScript handles:

Form submission

Email/password validation

Success/failure messaging

Demo credentials check

Social login (disabled in demo mode)

🚀 How to Run
Clone or download the repo

Open login.html in any web browser

Enter demo credentials and click Sign In

🔮 Planned Improvements
Connect with #Firebase or #Supabase

Enable #OAuthLogin (Google, Facebook)

Add #ForgotPassword and #SessionStorage

👨‍🎨 UI Design
Mobile-first layout

Branded with boAt theme

Gradient backgrounds and shadows

Accessible and keyboard-friendly inputs

